- Avoid putting secrets in `RHAPSODY.md`; use `$VAR` indirection only where explicitly supported.
- Decide whether project config lives in env vars first or in a local config file later.
- Production should fail closed when critical secrets are missing.
- Keep the singleton project shape easy to migrate to multi-project later.
